@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xwvkwf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(v0))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = ((tmp / (v2 + 0.71 / v0 + 0.66)) + 0.99)
    v2 = 0.76
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.71 * tmp + 0.54)) + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
